/li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/184_AC\" title=\"184 AC\">184</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/196_AC\" title=\"196 AC\">196</a></li></ul>\n</div></td></tr></tbody></table><div>\n</div></td></tr><tr style=\"height:2px\"><td></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"width:100%;padding:0px;;;\" class=\"navbox-list navbox-odd\"><div style=\"padding:0em 0.25em\">\n</div><table cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"nowraplinks collapsible uncollapsed navbox-subgroup\" style=\"border-spacing:0;width:100%;;;;\"><tbody><tr><th scope=\"col\" style=\";\" class=\"navbox-title\" colspan=\"2\"><span style=\"float:left;width:6em;\">&#160;</span><div class=\"\" style=\"font-size:110%;\">\nThird century since Aegon's Conquest</div></th></tr><tr style=\"height:2px;\"><td></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"width:100%;padding:0px;;;\" class=\"navbox-list navbox-odd\"><div style=\"padding:0em 0.25em\">\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/209_AC\" title=\"209 AC\">209</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/211_AC\" title=\"211 AC\">211</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/212_AC\" title=\"212 AC\">212</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/219_AC\" title=\"219 AC\">219</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/233_AC\" title=\"233 AC\">233</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/236_AC\" title=\"236 AC\">236</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/259_AC\" title=\"259 AC\">259</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/260_AC\" title=\"260 AC\">260</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/261_AC\" title=\"261 AC\">261</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/262_AC\" title=\"262 AC\">262</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/280_AC\" title=\"280 AC\">280</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/281_AC\" title=\"281 AC\">281</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/282_AC\" title=\"282 AC\">282</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/283_AC\" title=\"283 AC\">283</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/284_AC\" title=\"284 AC\">284</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/285_AC\" title=\"285 AC\">285</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/289_AC\" title=\"289 AC\">289</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/290_AC\" title=\"290 AC\">290</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/295_AC\" title=\"295 AC\">295</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/297_AC\" title=\"297 AC\">297</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/298_AC\" title=\"298 AC\">298</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/299_AC\" title=\"299 AC\">299</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/300_AC\" title=\"300 AC\">300</a></li></ul>\n</div></td></tr></tbody></table><div>\n</div></td></tr></tbody></table></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><br />\n</p>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:212px;\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Shen-fei-jaehaerys-proclaimed.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/thumb/1/14/Shen-fei-jaehaerys-proclaimed.jpg/210px-Shen-fei-jaehaerys-proclaimed.jpg\" width=\"210\" height=\"199\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/1/14/Shen-fei-jaehaerys-proclaimed.jpg/315px-Shen-fei-jaehaerys-proclaimed.jpg 1.5x, /images/thumb/1/14/Shen-fei-jaehaerys-proclaimed.jpg/420px-Shen-fei-jaehaerys-proclaimed.jpg 2x\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Shen-fei-jaehaerys-proclaimed.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>Jaehaerys proclaimed king by Shen Fei for <i><a href=\"/index.php/The_Rise_of_the_Dragon\" title=\"The Rise of the Dragon\">The Rise of the Dragon</a></i></div></div></div>\n<p><b>Year 48 After the Conquest</b> (<b>48 AC</b>) is a year in the <a href=\"/index.php/Years_after_Aegon%27s_Conquest\" title=\"Years after Aegon&#39;s Conquest\">Westerosi calendar</a>, the 48th after <a href=\"/index.php/Aegon_I_Targaryen\" title=\"Aegon I Targaryen\">Aegon</a>'s crowning in <a href=\"/index.php/Oldtown\" title=\"Oldtown\">Oldtown</a> that maesters and educated people use as a reference to date the years.\n</p><p>In 48 AC Maegor the Cruel's reign crumbled down, with widespread revolts against him. House Tully openly defied him joining <a href=\"/index.php/Outlaw\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Outlaw\">outlaw</a> Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Joffrey_Doggett\" title=\"Joffrey Doggett\">Joffrey Doggett</a>, Septon <a href=\"/index.php/Moon_(septon)\" title=\"Moon (septon)\">Moon</a> marched towards Oldtown followed by thousands of followers and supported by lords Rowan and Oakheart, and his nephew <a href=\"/index.php/Jaehaerys_I_Targaryen\" title=\"Jaehaerys I Targaryen\">Jaehaerys Targaryen</a> was proclaimed king with the support of Storm's End. Most of his supporters abandoned him, including his Hand Lord Celtigar and his Great Maester Benifer. His master of ships, two of his kingsguard and his own wife Rhaena deserted him and went over to Jaehaerys. Lords Hightower, Lannister and Arryn also joined Jaehaerys cause. With only a few lesser lords left supporting him, Maegor nonetheless made his battle plans but was found dead on the Iron Throne the next morning. \n</p><p>Jaehaerys I spent the remaining of the year restoring the relationships between the crown and the Faith. After the convenient death of Septon Moon, the young king was crowned and anointed at Oldtown.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Deaths\">Deaths</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=48_AC&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Deaths\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:212px;\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Maegor_kills_Tyanna_by_Kieran_Yanner_(The_Rise_of_the_Dragon).jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/thumb/a/a3/Maegor_kills_Tyanna_by_Kieran_Yanner_%28The_Rise_of_the_Dragon%29.jpg/210px-Maegor_kills_Tyanna_by_Kieran_Yanner_%28The_Rise_of_the_Dragon%29.jpg\" width=\"210\" height=\"279\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/a/a3/Maegor_kills_Tyanna_by_Kieran_Yanner_%28The_Rise_of_the_Dragon%29.jpg/315px-Maegor_kills_Tyanna_by_Kieran_Yanner_%28The_Rise_of_the_Dragon%29.jpg 1.5x, /images/thumb/a/a3/Maegor_kills_Tyanna_by_Kieran_Yanner_%28The_Rise_of_the_Dragon%29.jpg/420px-Maegor_kills_Tyanna_by_Kieran_Yanner_%28The_Rise_of_the_Dragon%29.jpg 2x\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Maegor_kills_Tyanna_by_Kieran_Yanner_(The_Rise_of_the_Dragon).jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>Maegor cuts out Tyanna's heart by Kieran Yanner for <i><a href=\"/index.php/The_Rise_of_the_Dragon\" title=\"The Rise of the Dragon\">The Rise of the Dragon</a></i></div></div></div>\n<ul><li>Queen <a href=\"/index.php/Jeyne_Westerling_(wife_of_Maegor_I)\" title=\"Jeyne Westerling (wife of Maegor I)\">Jeyne Westerling</a> dies after going into labour three months early, delivering a malformed stillborn child.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiaf_the_targaryen_kings:_maegor_i.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiaf_the_targaryen_kings:_maegor_i.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabthe_sons_of_the_dragon.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabthe_sons_of_the_dragon.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Tyanna_of_the_Tower\" title=\"Tyanna of the Tower\">Tyanna of the Tower</a>, killed by King Maegor I Targaryen. <sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiaf_the_targaryen_kings:_maegor_i.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiaf_the_targaryen_kings:_maegor_i.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtsotd.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtsotd.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li>King <a href=\"/index.php/Maegor_I_Targaryen\" title=\"Maegor I Targaryen\">Maegor I Targaryen</a> dies on the <a href=\"/index.php/Iron_Throne\" title=\"Iron Throne\">Iron Throne</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragotappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragotappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtsotd.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtsotd.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li>Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Owen_Bush\" title=\"Owen Bush\">Owen Bush</a> found dead and mutilated in <a href=\"/index.php/King%27s_Landing\" title=\"King&#39;s Landing\">King's Landing</a>. <sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtsotd.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtsotd.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li>Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Maladon_Moore\" title=\"Maladon Moore\">Maladon Moore</a>, executed by <a href=\"/index.php/Jaehaerys_I_Targaryen\" title=\"Jaehaerys I Targaryen\">Jaehaerys I Targaryen</a>.</li>\n<li>Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Harrold_Langward\" title=\"Harrold Langward\">Harrold Langward</a> slain by <a href=\"/index.php/Gyles_Morrigen\" title=\"Gyles Morrigen\">Gyles Morrigen</a> in <a href=\"/index.php/Trial_by_combat\" title=\"Trial by combat\">trial by combat</a>.</li>\n<li>Lord <a href=\"/index.php/House_Rosby\" title=\"House Rosby\">Rosby</a>, drank hemlock.</li>\n<li>Septon <a href=\"/index.php/Moon_(septon)\" title=\"Moon (septon)\">Moon</a>, stabbed at his own camp.</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Lorcas_the_Learned\" title=\"Lorcas the Learned\">Lorcas the Learned</a>, after he foolishly attacked <a href=\"/index.php/Oldtown\" title=\"Oldtown\">Oldtown</a>.</li>\n<li>All of Maegors headsmen, gaolers and confessors for the crimes they committed under Maegor's reign.</li></ul>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Titles_and_Positions\">Titles and Positions</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=48_AC&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Titles and Positions\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<ul><li>Prince Jaehaerys Targaryen is crowned as King <a href=\"/index.php/Jaehaerys_I_Targaryen\" title=\"Jaehaerys I Targaryen\">Jaehaerys I Targaryen</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragotappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragotappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup></li></ul>\n<p><b>Small Council</b>\n</p>\n<ul><li>Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Rogar_Baratheon\" title=\"Rogar Baratheon\">Rogar Baratheon</a> is named <a href=\"/index.php/Hand_of_the_King\" title=\"Hand of the King\">Hand of the King</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Protector_of_the_Realm\" title=\"Protector of the Realm\">Protector of the Realm</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabprince_into_king_-_the_ascension_of_jaehaerys_i.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_5-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabprince_into_king_-_the_ascension_of_jaehaerys_i.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Alyssa_Velaryon\" title=\"Alyssa Velaryon\">Alyssa Velaryon</a> is named <a href=\"/index.php/Regent\" title=\"Regent\">Queen Regent</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabprince_into_king_-_the_ascension_of_jaehaerys_i.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_5-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabprince_into_king_-_the_ascension_of_jaehaerys_i.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Benifer\" title=\"Benifer\">Benifer</a> is reinstated as <a href=\"/index.php/Maester\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Maester\">Grand Maester</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabprince_into_king_-_the_ascension_of_jaehaerys_i.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_5-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabprince_into_king_-_the_ascension_of_jaehaerys_i.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Daemon_Velaryon_(son_of_Aethan)\" title=\"Daemon Velaryon (son of Aethan)\">Daemon Velaryon</a> is named <a href=\"/index.php/Master_of_ships\" title=\"Master of ships\">master of ships</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabprince_into_king_-_the_ascension_of_jaehaerys_i.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_5-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabprince_into_king_-_the_ascension_of_jaehaerys_i.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Edwell_Celtigar\" title=\"Edwell Celtigar\">Edwell Celtigar</a> is named <a href=\"/index.php/Master_of_coin\" title=\"Master of coin\">master of coin</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabprince_into_king_-_the_ascension_of_jaehaerys_i.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_5-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabprince_into_king_-_the_ascension_of_jaehaerys_i.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup></li></ul>\n<p><b>Kingsguard</b>\n</p>\n<ul><li>Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Gyles_Morrigen\" title=\"Gyles Morrigen\">Gyles Morrigen</a> is named to the <a href=\"/index.php/Kingsguard\" title=\"Kingsguard\">Kingsguard</a> as its <a href=\"/index.php/Lord_Commander_of_the_Kingsguard\" title=\"Lord Commander of the Kingsguard\">Lord Commander</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabprince_into_king_-_the_ascension_of_jaehaerys_i.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_5-5\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabprince_into_king_-_the_ascension_of_jaehaerys_i.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li>Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Joffrey_Doggett\" title=\"Joffrey Doggett\">Joffrey Doggett</a> is named to the <a href=\"/index.php/Kingsguard\" title=\"Kingsguar